column2: >Meet Alfie, our friendly and lovable rabbit dressed in smart corduroy dungarees and a soft teal coloured knitted jumper. Presented in his own embroidered linen bag.

>Alfie is the 35cms version of our large Alfie Rabbit, who has proved to be so popular we decided to make a friend for our 35 cms Fifi! He is dressed with the same care and attention  to detail with soft corduroy dungarees and a practical knitted jumper.

>Baby Alfie Rattle soft toy is dressed in soft chunky corduroy dungarees and a teal knitted jumper. Made from the fluffiest beige coloured velour , he will be the perfect companion for your baby in the pram. Give Baby Alfie a gentle shake to hear her delicate rattle.

>Baby Bo Rabbit is just as lovable and will delight any child for many years to come. Baby Bo is made in the same gorgeous fur, has a weighted torso, and comes with an embroidered identification patch on the sole of the paw. Baby Bo arrives in a beautiful presentation box.

>Baby Darcy is just the right size for a traveling companion, whether its home or abroad. The attention to detail is just the same as on the larger version of Darcy with a velvety brown nose, embroidered eyes and an identification patch. Baby Darcy arrives in a beautiful presentation box.

>Delightful Baby Fifi Rattle soft toy is made from the softest velour and 100% cotton yarn which has been sourced for her hand-knitted dress. A floral ribbon is threaded through the dress completing her pretty look. Give Baby Fifi a gentle shake to hear her delicate rattle.
